Usage
-----

Fetch all the 'cvc log'
    $ ./get-all-pkg-log foresight.rpath.org@fl:2-devel /tmp/cvc-history

Convert to git:
    $ cat /tmp/cvc-history/sources-list | cut -d: -f1 | xargs ./cvc2git --history-dir=/tmp/cvc-history/logs --git-dir=/tmp/cvc2git/

---

Refresh the 'cvc log' cache:
    $ ./get-all-pkg-log --refresh foresight.rpath.org@fl:2-devel /tmp/cvc-history

Fetch 'cvc log' for one package:
    # ./get-pkg-log zenity:source=foresight.rpath.org@fl:1-devel > some/file

Pick packages to convert:
    $ ./cvc2git --history-dir=/tmp/cvc-history/logs --git-dir=/tmp/cvc2git/ pilot-link rapid-photo-downloader rapidsvn raptor group-desktop-platform

Refresh the git repo:
    $ cat /tmp/cvc-history/sources-list | cut -d: -f1 | xargs ./cvc2git --history-dir=/tmp/cvc-history/logs --git-dir=/tmp/cvc2git/ --refresh

